text: Dave Considine is an American educator and politician. Born in Janesville, Wisconsin, Considine grew up in North Prairie, Wisconsin and graduated from Mukwonago High School. He received his bachelor's degree in education from University of Wisconsin-Whitewater and his masters in education from Viterbo University. He then taught school in the Baraboo School District for 29 years. On November 4, 2014.
